decks.notes: This Mono Black Aggro deck focuses on aggressive creature and disruption spells to quickly take control of the game. With a mix of powerful creatures like Scrapheap Scrounger and Spawn of Mayhem, along with removal spells like Fatal Push and Murderous Rider, the deck aims to apply pressure early on while disrupting the opponent's game plan. Thoughtseize and Liliana of the Veil provide additional disruption, allowing the deck to maintain its tempo and outpace the opponent. Overall, the deck aims to win through efficient aggression and disruption, overwhelming opponents with its early threats.
